text:
Kiriko, I received some of the photos
we took the other day.

Wow...
Is it okay if I see them...?

They're all well taken, aren't they?
Hmm, this one has a very natural expression.

Thank you...
Um... During the shoot...

The camera... sounded like...
it was talking to me... *click, click*...

Oh, really...! Then this must be the expression of
someone enjoying a pleasant conversation...!

Hehe... Perhaps...
That could be it...
